---
---

<section class="relative min-h-[400px] overflow-hidden bg-[#F5F5F0] p-10">

  <!-- マスク検証: shape.svg + bg_original.png -->
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="pointer-events-none absolute top-0 left-0 z-0 w-[min(72vw,540px)]"
    style="aspect-ratio: 500 / 331;"
  >
    <div
      class="h-full w-full"
      style="
        background-image: url('/img/bg_original.png');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        -webkit-mask-image: url('/img/shape.svg');
        mask-image: url('/img/shape.svg');
        -webkit-mask-repeat: no-repeat;
        mask-repeat: no-repeat;
        -webkit-mask-position: center;
        mask-position: center;
        -webkit-mask-size: contain;
        mask-size: contain;
        -webkit-mask-mode: alpha;
        mask-mode: alpha;
      "
    ></div>
  </div>

  <!-- 確認テキスト -->
  <div class="relative z-10 text-slate-700">
    <p class="font-bold">背景画像（bg_original.png）をシェイプマスク（shape.svg）で切り抜き</p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm">↑ 左側に画像がシェイプ形状で表示されるはず</p>
  </div>

  <!-- 以下は個別パーツの単体確認 -->
  <div class="relative z-10 mt-80 flex gap-8 flex-wrap">


    <!-- 1: 画像だけ（マスクなし） -->
    <div>
      <p class="mb-2 text-xs font-bold text-slate-500">① bg_original.png（マスクなし）</p>
      <div class="h-40 w-60 border border-slate-300"
        style="background-image: url('/img/bg_original.png'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- 2: shape.svg だけ（imgタグ） -->
    <div>
      <p class="mb-2 text-xs font-bold text-slate-500">② shape.svg（imgタグ）</p>
      <img src="/img/shape.svg" class="h-40 w-60 border border-slate-300 bg-white" alt="shape" />
    </div>

    <!-- 3: mask-mode: luminance（デフォルト動作確認） -->
    <div>
      <p class="mb-2 text-xs font-bold text-slate-500">③ mask-mode: luminance</p>
      <div
        class="h-40 w-60"
        style="
          background-image: url('/img/bg_original.png');
          background-size: cover;
          background-position: center;
          -webkit-mask-image: url('/img/shape.svg');
          mask-image: url('/img/shape.svg');
          -webkit-mask-size: contain;
          mask-size: contain;
          -webkit-mask-repeat: no-repeat;
          mask-repeat: no-repeat;
          -webkit-mask-mode: luminance;
          mask-mode: luminance;
        "
      ></div>
    </div>

    <!-- 4: mask-mode: alpha -->
    <div>
      <p class="mb-2 text-xs font-bold text-slate-500">④ mask-mode: alpha</p>
      <div
        class="h-40 w-60"
        style="
          background-image: url('/img/bg_original.png');
          background-size: cover;
          background-position: center;
          -webkit-mask-image: url('/img/shape.svg');
          mask-image: url('/img/shape.svg');
          -webkit-mask-size: contain;
          mask-size: contain;
          -webkit-mask-repeat: no-repeat;
          mask-repeat: no-repeat;
          -webkit-mask-mode: alpha;
          mask-mode: alpha;
        "
      ></div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
